Design a Prisma schema for this app.

Must support:
- Tickers (stocks, ETFs), pricing snapshots (daily), fundamentals (periodic)
- Articles: author, tickers mentioned, sections, tags, paywalled flag, source links
- Entities: people/institutions/analysts (e.g., Pelosi, Goldman), with type + profile
- Activity events unified table (Congress trades, insider trades, 13F changes, analyst actions)
- Watchlists + alert rules per user
- Source table to track provenance (url, publisher, retrieved_at)
- Optional: “signal scores” table for computed metrics

Output:
- Prisma models with indexes
- Short explanation of each model and why it exists
- Example queries needed by each page (Home/Stock/Article/Entity/Activity)